        "from": "T01n0026_046:0715c19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何行禪者熾盛則知熾盛如真？",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0715c19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼行禪者離欲、離惡不善之法，有覺、有觀，離生喜、樂，得初禪成就遊。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0715c21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼心修習正思，快樂息寂，則從初禪趣第二禪，是勝息寂。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0715c22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼行禪者便作是念：",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0715c23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我心修習正思，快樂息寂，則從初禪趣第二禪，是勝息寂。",
