        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，行禪者度一切無量識處，無所有，是無所有處成就遊。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼心修習正思，快樂息寂，從無所有處趣非有想非無想處，是勝息寂。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼行禪者便作是念：",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我心修習正思，快樂息寂，從無所有處趣非有想非無想處，是勝息寂。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b07_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』彼知如真已，便覺彼心而不失定，如是行禪者熾盛則知熾盛如真。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世間實有是四種行禪者，因此故說。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說如是。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行禪經第五竟二千五百七十七字177 說經（一七七）中阿含心品說經第六第四分別誦我聞如是：",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一時，佛遊拘樓瘦劒摩瑟曇拘樓都邑。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今當為汝等說法，初妙、中妙、竟亦妙，有義有文，具足清淨，顯現梵行，名四種說經。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如四種說經分別其義。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽，諦聽，善思念之，我今當說。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b19_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時，諸比丘受教而聽。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何四種說經分別其義？",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有比丘所行、所相、所標，離欲、離惡不善之法，有覺、有觀，離生喜、樂，得初禪成就遊。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼不受此行，不念此相、標，唯行欲樂相應念想退轉具。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼比丘應當知，『我生此法，不住、不進，亦復不厭，我生此法而令我退，然我此定不得久住。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b26_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』彼比丘應如是知。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b26_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，比丘所行、所相、所標，離欲、離惡不善之法，有覺、有觀，離生喜、樂，得初禪成就遊。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b28_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼受此行，念此相、標，立念如法，令住一意。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716b29_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼比丘應當知，『我生此法，不退、不進，亦復不厭，我生此法能令我住，而我此定必得久住。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716c03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』彼比丘應如是知。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716c03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，比丘所行、所相、所標，離欲、離惡不善之法，有覺、有觀，離生喜、樂，得初禪成就遊。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716c05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼不受此行，不念此相、標，唯行第二禪相應念想昇進具。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716c06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼比丘應當知，『我生此法，不退、不住，亦復不厭，我生此法令我昇進，如是不久當得第二禪。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716c09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』彼比丘應如是知。",
        "from": "T01n0026_046:0716c09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，比丘所行、所相、所標，離欲、離惡不善之法，有覺、有觀，離生喜、樂，得初離成就遊。",
